info.brief_description: The Invader Zim universe with vore. Female preds only. No male preds.
info.description:
My thought process for this was; I like vore, Ilike Invader Zim. why not combine the two?

So the rules are:
1. Keep it within that universe.
2. Females predators only. Sorry, but I don't like males eating living things.
3. No one line additions. (excluding choices)
4. OCs are permitted, as long as they aren't a Mary Sue or Gary Stu
5. If you feel like including romance, go ahead but Tak is off limits. She will always be with my character, Vipe.
6. i'll think of more later.
